description: This file declares APIs for accessing gateway information parameters in a data model related to network device management. It includes function prototypes for retrieving boolean, integer, unsigned long, and string parameter values associated with GatewayInfo objects.

methods.name: GatewayInfo_GetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Retrieves a boolean parameter value for GatewayInfo object.

methods.name: GatewayInfo_GetParamIntValue
methods.description: Retrieves an integer parameter value for GatewayInfo object.

methods.name: GatewayInfo_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves an unsigned long parameter value for GatewayInfo object.

methods.name: GatewayInfo_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves a string parameter value for GatewayInfo object.
